# Pur3v4d3r Imperial Theme

Professional Obsidian dark theme with red, grey, and black color scheme.

## ğŸ¨ Features

- **Monochromatic Palette**: Red (#E50000), Grey (#E0E0E0), Black (#0A0A0A)
- **Glassmorphism Sidebars**: Backdrop blur effects (Coming in Phase 6)
- **Advanced Code Blocks**: Dual-color borders with gradient backgrounds (Coming in Phase 3)
- **Unified Callout System**: 30 essential callout types with Card Elevated style (Coming in Phase 5)
- **Performance-Optimized**: Zero animations, smooth CSS transitions only
- **Clean CSS**: No !important flags, proper specificity hierarchy

